works.description: Photo of shopping cart against a silver car in a parking lot, overlaid with text in teal font color to match DiabloDents' website header and other images on site. Text says, "Because Dents Happen." Copyright is owned in full by DiabloDents, and no permission, either written or implied, was given to the infringing site authorizing its use there. Photo is on the left side of the infringing post, about 2/3 of the way down the page.
